        This option specifies what kind of backing store to give the window.
        The default is NNoottUUsseeffuull.
    --bbww pixels
        This option specifies the border width for the window.
    --ddiissppllaayy display
        This option specifies the X server to contact.
    --ggeeoommeettrryy geom
        This option specifies either or both the size and location of the
        window.
    --iidd windowid
        This option specifies that the window with the given id should be
